  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<ul><li>Supervise, motivate, and direct construction workers and subcontractors, assigning tasks and monitoring performance</li><li>Enforce strict safety regulations, conduct safety training, and ensure compliance with building codes and legal requirements</li><li>Plan daily activities, manage schedules, order materials, and ensure smooth workflow to keep projects on track</li><li>Inspect work, materials, and site conditions to ensure adherence to blueprints, specifications, and standards</li><li>Act as the main link between crews, engineers, architects, clients, and project managers, providing updates and resolving issues</li><li>Maintain detailed site records, progress reports, and handle essential paperwork</li><li>Staying up to date with safety codes and advancements in construction</li><li>Resolve workplace issues, conflicts, and escalated customer complaints</li></ul>",
